{"title":"Walking tome","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Walking_tome","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.28](/0.28 \"0.28\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n|   | A spellbook that has gone too long without being read. It overflows with magic, forming thick armour from its binding, legs from its pages, and periodically erupting in flurries of free-floating, self-casting spells. |\n\n**Walking tomes** are self-animated arcane constructs most notable for being able to [Conjure Living Spells](/Conjure_Living_Spells \"Conjure Living Spells\"). Much like [Foxfires](/Foxfire \"Foxfire\"), living spells will seek out nearby targets and attempt to ram into them, destroying themselves to inflict a magical effect. Fortunately, living spells are fragile and can be instantly dispersed with any sort of attack.\n\nWalking tomes may be found in the [Depths](/Depths \"Depths\") and [Tukima's Studio](/Tukima%27s_Studio \"Tukima's Studio\").\n\n## Walking tome types\n\n; [![Walking crystal tome.png](/images/2/29/Walking_crystal_tome.png)](/File:Walking_crystal_tome.png) **[Walking crystal tome](/Walking_crystal_tome \"Walking crystal tome\")** - Among the deadlier tomes, these books cast the highly-damaging [Lehudib's Crystal Spear](/Lehudib%27s_Crystal_Spear \"Lehudib's Crystal Spear\").\n\n; [![Walking divine tome.png](/images/2/24/Walking_divine_tome.png)](/File:Walking_divine_tome.png) **[Walking divine tome](/Walking_divine_tome \"Walking divine tome\")** - Their living [Smiting](/Smiting \"Smiting\") spells don't deal much damage individually, but bypass nearly all forms of defense and come in greater numbers.\n\n; [![Walking earthen tome.png](/images/d/dd/Walking_earthen_tome.png)](/File:Walking_earthen_tome.png) **[Walking earthen tome](/Walking_earthen_tome \"Walking earthen tome\")** - Living [Petrify](/Petrify \"Petrify\") spells might not do any damage, but will leave their victims helpless to avoid these tomes' surprisingly hefty physical strikes.\n\n; [![Walking frostbound tome.png](/images/3/34/Walking_frostbound_tome.png)](/File:Walking_frostbound_tome.png) **[Walking frostbound tome](/Walking_frostbound_tome \"Walking frostbound tome\")** - These tomes create mayhem with flurries of living [Iceblast](/Iceblast \"Iceblast\") spells.\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Walking tome - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Walking_tome\",\"wgTitle\":\"Walking tome\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":71284,\"wgRevisionId\":71284,\"wgArticleId\":10714,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.28 articles\",\"Lists of monsters\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",